    "hed": "What happened at Lake Oroville?",
    "byline": "By <a href=\"mailto:eoneill@sfchronicle.com\">Emma O'Neill</a>, <a href=\"mailto:jblanchard@sfchronicle.com\">John Blanchard</a>, and <a href=\"mailto:kalexander@sfchronicle.com\">Kurtis Alexander</a>"
